TORRES v. WARDEN OF THE MARYLAND PENITENTIARY [App. No. 74,

September Term, 1965.]

Decided January 6, 1966. Before Prescott, C. -J., and Hammond, Marbury, Oppenheimer and McWilliams, JJ. ..... Per Curiam.

Application for leave to appeal from á denial.of post.conviction relief is denied for the reasons set out in the opinion of Judge Harlan in the court below.

Application denied.
